><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mtf1665702755765.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mtf1665702755765.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mtf1665702755765.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mtf1665702755765\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Deletes the specified document from storage.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__topic_d127553e1_d127554e1_d127555e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__p_d127556e1_d127557e1_d127558e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.datastore.remove</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Doc</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__p_d127559e1_d127560e1_d127561e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.datastore.remove</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">_id:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Rev</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__p_d127562e1_d127563e1_d127564e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.datastore.remove(doc._id, doc._rev);</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__section_w1391ab1b5b3_w1392ab1b5_w1393ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d630089e98\">Arguments </h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__parml_vy5_vtb_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Doc</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Document object to remove. </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">DocId</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Identifier of the document to delete, in the format <code class=\"ph codeph\">_id:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> (or <var class=\"keyword varname\">Doc</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">._id</code>) </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Rev</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Revision of the document to delete, in the format <code class=\"ph codeph\">_rev:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> (or <var class=\"keyword varname\">Doc</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">._rev</code>) </dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__section_w1394ab1b5b5_w1395ab1b5_w1396ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d630089e158\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__p_d127571e1_d127572e1_d127573e1\">Returns a JavaScript Promise object with the response.\n        For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__codeblock_vdj_d5b_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">{\n \"ok\": true\n }</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Otherwise, an error is returned. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__section_ivv_5sv_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d630089e173\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword apiname\">remove()</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__p_d127580e1_d127581e1_d127582e1\">There are two ways to specify the document to be\n        deleted from client-side storage:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__ul_hhk_f5b_dwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__li_d46274e1_d46275e1_d46276e1\">Specify the whole document:\n          <div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mtf1665702755765_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__codeblock_dj4_g5b_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp').then(function(doc) {\n return uniface.datastore.remove(doc);\n }).then(function (result) {\n // handle result\n }).catch(function (err) {\n console.log(err);\n });</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__li_d46277e1_d46278e1_d46279e1\">Specify the document ID and revision:\n          <div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mtf1665702755765_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mtf1665702755765__codeblock_vsm_h5b_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp').then(function(doc) {\n return uniface.datastore.remove(doc._id, doc._rev);\n }).then(function (result) {\n // handle result\n }).catch(function (err) {\n console.log(err);\n });</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530065\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530065\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "remove() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Deletes the specified document from storage. uniface.datastore.remove ( Doc ) uniface.datastore.remove ( _id: String , Rev ) Example: uniface.datastore.remove(doc._id, doc._rev); Arguments Doc Document object to remove. DocId Identifier of the document to delete, in the format _id: String (or Doc ._id ) Rev Revision of the document to delete, in the format _rev: String (or Doc ._rev ) Return Value Returns a JavaScript Promise object with the response. For example: { \"ok\": true } Copy Otherwise, an error is returned. Example: Using remove() There are two ways to specify the document to be deleted from client-side storage: Specify the whole document: Explain this code uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp').then(function(doc) { return uniface.datastore.remove(doc); }).then(function (result) { // handle result }).catch(function (err) { console.log(err); }); Copy Specify the document ID and revision: Explain this code uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp').then(function(doc) { return uniface.datastore.remove(doc._id, doc._rev); }).then(function (result) { // handle result }).catch(function (err) { console.log(err); }); Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}